channel.title: Runescape private server
channel.description:
Hi everyone I would like to pay someone to make me a private server. How good you make will determine the price. I will pay 10-25$.
Requirements.
-Must have the same weapons as todays servers. -Must have skilling teleports. -Must have a guide on commands or codes i and mods will know, a detailed description on how everything works. -Must have other specs that any other server has. -I would really like good shops with weapons in it. No chaotic stores or any "Really" good weapons.
I hope these requirements arent that hard. Please pm me back or type a comment below VVVVVVVVVV. Ty for your help.
